  "description": "A squirrel clings upside down to a tree branch against a brilliant blue sky. The squirrel is mid-movement, its body curved and paws gripping the branch. Its long, bushy tail curves gracefully downwards. The branch it clings to has budding leaves, hinting at springtime, with small pink and green buds visible. The background is a clear, cloudless blue sky, emphasizing the squirrel and branch as the central focus. The lighting is bright and direct, illuminating the squirrel's fur and the texture of the branch.",
